 Functional Responsibilities
List the core functionalities the microservice is responsible for.

Responsibility	Description
Consume Event A	Listen to queue/topic X, process incoming messages
Validate Payload	Validate required fields, business rules
Transform & Enrich	Add metadata or enrich with DB/external call
Produce Event B	Publish result to topic Y
Persist Data	Save/update to DB if needed


